{"tid":1849354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（回帶）午餐肉潮文-改","createTime":"2020-01-29T04:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T11:08:25.000Z","uid":219183,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"436942e32e1626ecefc8df08e765124af8a8887d","tid":1849354,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:16:11.000Z","msg":"2012又好，928又好，山竹又好，支国肺炎又好，有咩事發生都唔驚，只要鳩縮唔出街都實有命有得食~~<br />\n當然，到有日真係出現全香港範圍MAP炮就咩都唔使<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xt7jPSm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXt7jPSm.jpg&h=504e28c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2P6Aocq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2P6Aocq.jpg&h=dfa625e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放喺廚房櫃嘅罐頭同米，米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿，到中國午餐肉，回煱肉，豆，菜，金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KZusEj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7KZusEj.jpg&h=5088fcd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一箱箱未開，太多，放到出廳 [依啲全部係魚]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QZFzjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QZFzjw.jpg&h=55da76a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水污染，未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐，依家啲水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OzwHNEV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOzwHNEV.jpg&h=795ef6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即食麵 有5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外，打邊爐石油氣有存貨21支、外科口罩30盒、止痛止咳丸各15盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無野食~~無醫生睇嘅日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待手持午餐肉就可以有閪屌嘅日子"},{"pid":"1567ba7de96c5eb5ecdb16be4a3317e54fca62ee","tid":1849354,"uid":9640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjrMrcp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjrMrcp.jpg&h=e20e71f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇傳媒及出版嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n組織工會 全面罷工</span></span><br />\n- - -<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［港共不封關，全港冚家剷］香港傳媒及出版職工會-籌組中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847821\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n又一個工會準備誕生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路過入黎幫手推個post  謝謝<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5bc618199130553c5d559763d5ad7779c0589c0b","tid":1849354,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1567ba7de96c5eb5ecdb16be4a3317e54fca62ee","tid":1849354,"uid":9640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjrMrcp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjrMrcp.jpg&h=e20e71f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇傳媒及出版嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n組織工會 全面罷工</span></span><br />\n- - -<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［港共不封關，全港冚家剷］香港傳媒及出版職工會-籌組中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847821\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n又一個工會準備誕生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路過入黎幫手推個post  謝謝<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:24:34.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea57b408104dca4d22a83287dfa3ac084d26739","tid":1849354,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas